greeableness"], "rationale": "Practitioner Pharma Production, QA/QC and Validation - Production Officer benefits from conscientiousness, extraversion, agreeableness because the role requires disciplined evidence handling, careful exception tracking, stable follow-through and communication across production, quality, engineering, maintenance, supplier, lab or customer owners. These traits should adjust confidence and coaching focus, not act as a hard exclusion rule."}'::jsonb, '{"values": ["Impact", "Security", "Leadership"], "rationale": "Practitioner Pharma Production, QA/QC and Validation - Production Officer aligns best with learners who value impact, security, leadership because the role environment involves visible manufacturing output, stable operating discipline, accountable quality outcomes and ownership of closure evidence. Work values should be used to prioritise role options, not to prove technical ability."}'::jsonb, 'Preferred', 'B.Pharm; M.Pharm; B.Sc Chemistry; Microbiology; Biotechnology; Mechanical; Electrical; Instrumentation', true),
